Feature: create project

  Background: set connection to pivotal tracker API REST
    Given I have set a connection to pivotal tracker API service

  Scenario: Get projects
    Given I have a set of projects
    When I send a GET request to /projects endpoint
    Then I expect the status code 200
  @project
  Scenario: Create project
    Given I have the next parameters to create a project:

      | name   | test name |
      | public | true      |

    When I send a POST request to /projects endpoint
    Then I expect the status code 200
